A locked door...

((This is a Job System resource. Click to interact.))
This post has a pair of manacles bolted to it. Judging by the corpses nearby, the denizens of these caves pass their time by chaining captives here and beating them to death.
This looks to be the mutilated remains of a halfling. His arms end in bloody stumps, hands still hanging from the shackles on the post he died by.

A vibrant patch of fire lichen...

((This is a Job System resource. Click to interact.))

This patch of fireweed almost seems hot to the touch...

((This is a Job System resource. Click to interact.))
This magically-enchanted cold storage chest seems to be brimming with all manner of ill-gotten goods.

You barely manage to crack the door before a nauseating stench hits you. The dim light from the nearby fire affords a look at a festering wallow of filth the beastmen call a hut, walls plastered with blood and vomit. A lingering smell of stale urine follows you even after you back away.
